Package: surveycto
Type: Package
Title: Manipulation of Data Collected through XLSFORM-compliant Platforms
Version: 0.1.0
Author@R: c(person("Waiguru Muiruki", email="waigurusamuel@gmail.com"
Maintainer: The package maintainer <waigurusamuel@gmail.com>
Description: SurveyCTO package is a metapackages that is comprised of 
             specilized function to organize, manipulate and analyze
             data collected through platform that use XLSFORM compliant
             platforms such as SurveyCTO,ODK, ONA,Kobotoolbox.However, 
             some function(s) may be used with any structured.  The main
             is to develop live dashboard during data collection.
             There are functions to add value labels for both multiple 
             and single variables from XLSFORM.
